{
  "stem": "17606.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Give us-- they-- they put us under the chuppah and give us this-- [INAUDIBLE] blessings for the-- marriage blessings.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And according to Jewish law, you don't need a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Any Jew can do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You see, so much I knew of the Jewish law.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had quite a number of guests.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had already people with guns staying outside and watching.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] was at my wedding.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's where we-- [INAUDIBLE] was negotiating with the two groups to get together.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he said, I would love to.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I said, blessed were the days when I was a member of [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I learned how to hold a gun in my hand.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now, I can teach the Jewish pacifist something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I didn't come to anything, because of the [NON-ENGLISH], the extreme left group [INAUDIBLE] come to this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] who didn't want it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they both didn't want it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before that, still before September this, the-- the ghetto was cut smaller.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then it was-- one part of the ghetto was taken out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was called the small ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] And we had to move from where we were to another part of the ghetto, central ghetto next to-- actually, we moved next to the headquarters of the Jewish military organization the [INAUDIBLE] 7.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we-- and we lived in [INAUDIBLE] 5, which was very convenient for me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then in January 18, it was a new action.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They started-- and until today, I don't know if this was planned for three days, or just because we responded.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was when the first shots-- Jewish shots were fired.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And that's-- [INAUDIBLE] I don't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "After two-- two or three days, they abandoned the action.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I am-- I am not sure.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] thanks to us.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
